    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The activity characterized by rhythmical skipping and stepping, with regular turnings and movements of the limbs and body, usually to the accompaniment of music.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
